archetypes.title: The Individualist
archetypes.description: Your primary drive is the pursuit of inner truth and sudden insights.
archetypes.secondary_description: You bring a unique, independent streak to everything you do, ensuring that your primary actions always remain true to your own internal rhythm.

archetypes.title: The Truth Seeker
archetypes.description: Your primary drive is the pursuit of inner truth and sudden insights.
archetypes.secondary_description: An undercurrent of deep intuition and 'aha' moments follows you, often providing sudden clarity to your primary goals and decisions.

archetypes.title: The Steward
archetypes.description: Your life is built around the protection and nurturing of your immediate family, team, or community.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry a deep sense of inner knowing that flavors your primary actions with intuition and mystery.

archetypes.title: The Logic Master
archetypes.description: Your primary drive is the pursuit of inner truth and sudden insights.
archetypes.secondary_description: You possess a secondary drive for order and efficiency, often looking for patterns or improvements in the background of your main pursuits.

archetypes.title: The Storyteller
archetypes.description: Your primary drive is the pursuit of inner truth and sudden insights.
archetypes.secondary_description: Your journey is flavored by a need to reflect on past lessons, allowing you to bring a wealth of lived experience and wisdom to your primary role.

archetypes.title: The Catalyst
archetypes.description: Your primary drive is the pursuit of inner truth and sudden insights.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry a pulsing, transformative energy that tends to spark change and innovation in others, even when you aren't consciously trying to.
